I am recently joined in this group.

I have got a problem with Testing wizard builtin with Jbuilder7.

when I try to create testcase for one class , it says "problem 
creating testcase! you must be able to build the project".

But actually, there is no problem on building the project, and I am 
able to create testcases for other classes inside the same package!

the class of interest is also working fine in the project.

did anybody already experience this problem?

please help!!
